{"tid":330124,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"D肥人真係好黑人憎","createTime":"2017-07-21T02:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T11:34:08.000Z","uid":27510,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"597c9431bb265ca5ac119d1135b185ec08ed2ceb","tid":330124,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:07:49.000Z","msg":"話說我返工果到, 得我同另一個同事係坐同一間房<br />\n其他人都係坐第2到<br />\n同我同房果位同事係勁肥 (大約20個我咁肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n咁其實我返呢份工之前一直都冇話特別歧視D肥人<br />\n但返左一排已經變到勁憎佢<br />\n<br />\n例子1:<br />\n我之前開到房個冷氣到23, 24度左右<br />\n呢位同事成撚日話好熱, 吹到條街仲涼過間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後仲係到發我脾氣比面色我睇<br />\n我有同佢因為冷氣而嘈過<br />\n點知仲比佢話咁都唔覺得熱係我溫感有問題<br />\n話我個人自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 叫我帶外套著咪得囉etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗: 你減下肥咪唔覺熱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (只係心諗, 我廢事人身攻擊人)<br />\n<br />\n好啦咁我退一步, 帶件薄薄地外套返工著<br />\n點知佢見我有嬲著就同我較到個冷氣到16度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係16度呀, ON9 !<br />\n痴撚線, 當左間房係雪櫃咩<br />\n連其他同事間中入黎講工作上既野都話: 哇, 好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲要話同人講話只係覺得岩岩好, 想再較低D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (但已經係最低, 冇得再較)<br />\n<br />\n咁日日咁吹法, 我上星期終於吹病左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢見我係咁打黑痴, 就收斂左, 較到20度 (真係多撚謝晒)<br />\n到前幾日我好返少少, 廢事又吹親啦<br />\n就帶左件U記冬天有毛毛果件外廁嬲返去著 <br />\n(我買果陣真係冇諗過我會係夏天著呢件野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n點知佢見我帶左件咁厚既嬲, 即刻又較返16度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c2903e8a5524dbb23bc908d055a79a3365d14a","tid":330124,"uid":10667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"屌9佢 死肥閪 咁撚多脂肪熱你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去減肥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a804f3666e8fb456acc46124eb452e86f2e70882","tid":330124,"uid":127795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"洗撚忍佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a78c1a07538626d907eedf56ee845e3a63f09c","tid":330124,"uid":60007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"20個你咁撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51428a5876122d142174bd3903e3d50c30dbc6c","tid":330124,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌9佢 死肥閪 咁撚多脂肪熱你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去減肥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚佢打我, 我邊夠佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd25de6d311ae81a145d0db4d47717d84bffea5","tid":330124,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚忍佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上星期已經因為其他野同佢吵左大獲<br />\n(因為佢想爆我FACEBOOK, 比我發現仲要唔認, 發我老脾)<br />\n依家我地成個幾星期冇講過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95540e2106aba80f6fef1b235bdedcd744c5adfb","tid":330124,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20個你咁撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我講得誇張左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我80幾90磅, 佢我諗過200磅"},{"pid":"b0feeb713f468e88d93ffa2b10c1ba8a9a32f21b","tid":330124,"uid":10667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo